#originalStanceText=Yes
#originalTopic=Debate:_Right_to_bear_arms_in_the_US
The way to overcome historical American bias is to ensure every individual has the right to bear arms It is true that American history is filled with violence and bias towards ethnic minorities. However, the path to resolving this issue is to ensure every individual, regardless of class, race, or gender, has the right to bear arms, not to restrict that right to a militia.
